summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical underground distribution easements over portions of Balch's Wedgwood Park Addition No.3; Brookvale Garden Tracts; Saulsberry Beach Tracts, southeast quarter of Section 18, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M.: Loch-Gilvra Addition to the City of Seattle; Northeast Quarter of Section 7, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M.; Hood and Carr's First Addition to West Seattle; Lake Forest Park; and Lake Forest Park Third Addition.
